rooms.name: The Eldorian Foothills
rooms.description: The hills roll softly and the view is breathtaking.  Small woodland creatures scurry about and you feel at peace in this serene nature.  Open fields can be seen in the distance and a the Great Northern Road passes near here.  Looks like a good spot for a nap.

rooms.name: A Turn in the Great Northern Road
rooms.description: The road swings north and west here though the hills.  A small footpath departs from the road, cutting east through the scraggly grass.  It leads up higher into the hills toward a deeper forest.  The city of Anduin looms off to the southwest.

rooms.name: A Bend Leading to the Gates of Anduin
rooms.description: You are standing at the last bend in the Great Road between Anduin and the town of Mielikki.  The gates loom large in front of you to the south.  There are many guards around as well.
